## GIT WORKFLOW

Ogni Claude = worktree separato. Ogni fase = 1 PR.
`git worktree add ../[project]-C2 feature/[plan]-phase1`

## ORCHESTRATION

Launch: `~/.claude/scripts/claude-parallel.sh 3` (max 3 workers)
Send (kitty): `kitty @ send-text --match title:Claude-N "cmd"`
Send (tmux): `tmux send-keys -t claude-workers:Claude-N "cmd" Enter`

## RECOVERY

Se crash: leggi piano, trova ultimo checkpoint, riprendi.
`cat docs/plans/*.md | grep -A5 "CHECKPOINT LOG"`

## PR WORKFLOW

`git add . && git commit -m "feat: X" && git push -u origin feature/X`
`gh pr create --title "feat: X" --base main`

## STATUS LEGEND

⬜ Not started | 🔄 In progress | ✅ Done | ❌ Crashed/Blocked | 🔴 LOCKED | 🟢 UNLOCKED

